==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tropologize
<hw>Tro*pol"o*gize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To use in a
tropological sense, as a word; to make a trope of.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>If . . . Minerva be <qex>tropologized</qex> into prudence.</q>
<rj><qau>Cudworth.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tropology</ent>⟦br⟧
